description: Police confirmed that a 19-year-old man died at the scene of the crash in Grace Road, Crawley.
title: Driver, 19, dies in car crash
title_page: Driver, 19, dies in car crash in Crawley - BBC News
maintext:
A man has died in a single-vehicle crash in West Sussex, police have said.
The driver, a 19-year-old man, died at the scene in Grace Road, Crawley, at about 18:20 GMT on Saturday.
Police said there were no suspicious circumstances and that a report would be prepared for the coroner.
The man's next of kin have been informed.
